Villiform teeth in band on premaxilla and on dentary; 
1–3
rows on vomer; 
1–3
rows on the palatine; none on ectopterygoid, endopterygoid or basihyal.

Distribution. Known from Palau , the Marshall Islands and Fiji . We expect this species to be found elsewhere in the Caroline Islands and from Indonesia , New Guinea and other islands to Fiji (
Fig 14
).
